#8904
Ego System~
   Certain items (equipment, weapons, etc) that are endowed with special powers
or affects carry with them a rating known as an 'ego' value.  The more powerful
the item, the higher this ego value.  Player characters are assigned an ego
limit based on certain factors, and can not rent equipment in excess of that
limit.  (Note: the innkeepers will inform you that you have exceeded this limit
with the message: "I'm afraid I can not assure the safety of all of your items"
when you ask for an offer.  )

  The ego command informs you of how close you are to your ego limit.

Please continue to the north.
